Cast Aster Fixture is a deliberately small, self-authored test font family.
It is not copied from or derived from an external font.

The canonical source is source/generate_cast_aster_fixture.rs. The generator
writes the complete TrueType table directory, metadata, cmap, metrics, and
simple glyph outlines without consulting the clock, locale, network, host
font database, or random state. Both head timestamps are fixed to Unix epoch
1700000000 converted to the TrueType 1904 epoch.

Run misc/scripts/build-font-family-fixture-fonts.sh to regenerate the tracked
Regular and Bold files. The --check mode regenerates both files privately and
requires byte-for-byte equality with the tracked payloads.

The font family is licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1,
without a Reserved Font Name. The generator remains project source code.
